name: 米凯拉·明纳

last_movies.title: 糟糕厨子大改造 第二十七季

introduction: Micaela Minner was born in Dallas, TX. She is of African American decent from her father's side & Scottish, French, & English decent from her mother's side. She grew up playing competitive Fastpitch softball achieving a full ride scholarship to the University of Missouri. She got her B.A. in Communications-TV/Radio & then Masters degree. She owns a sports training facility & takes on-going acting classes & attends acting workshops. She enjoys riding her motorcycle, boxing, working out, and making people smile.
